Format
.author
Dave Schreiber 
.version
1.00
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
A 2.04-only replacement for the AmigaDOS Format command.  It uses a much
more complete Workbench user interface (allowing for greater control over
formatting from the Workbench) and is smaller that the original Format
command.  
